Sizes: 30”x40” and 42”x42”
Weight: 200GSM/7 oz
Material: Polyester Spandex Swaddle, Hemmed Fabric 
Printed on one side, the opposite side is solid white.

Our custom baby swaddles are made from soft and stretchy spandex fabric. Whether you''re seeking a delightful baby shower gift, a cozy newborn hospital outfit, or a stunning accessory for newborn photography, our swaddle has you covered. Our custom swaddle can be personalized with adorable designs, the baby''s name, or even a heartfelt message, making it a truly unique and cherished present for expectant parents.

Crafted with love and attention to detail, our spandex baby swaddle wraps your little one in a gentle, secure embrace. The breathable and flexible spandex material ensures maximum comfort, allowing your baby to rest peacefully and move freely. Wrap them in the love and comfort they deserve with our personalized swaddle, designed with adoration and attention to create unforgettable memories.

HOW TO ORDER
1. Select your Size and Material 
2. Choose a color from the Color Options photo
3. Choose the fonts from the Font Options photo
4. Review and confirm the mock up we will send via Etsy messages. 

* Please Note: All sizes have a variance +/- 1&quot;-2&quot; due to heat causing shrinking when pressed * Please review photos for size references!*

CARE INSTRUCTION To keep the fibers soft and silky over time, it is very important to avoid fabric softeners when washing this blanket. Many laundry pods contain softeners, and we recommend not using laundry pods for this item.  - Wash with detergent only, no fabric softeners - Wash in cold water - Gentle cycle - Wash separately to avoid lint transfer from other textiles - Tumble dry low and remove promptly

ADDITIONAL NOTES - Please keep in mind when ordering that color settings on monitors and lighting in product photography vary so the product might differ a tad from what you see on screen. - I don''t accept returns, exchanges, or cancellations. But please contact me if you have any problems with your order. - If you have any questions, please use the “Message Seller” button next to the price and I’ll get right back to you.', 39.99, 260, 'BS1003', 'active', '2023-11-21 21:37:20', '2023-12-07 20:41:26');

