- Vibrant, permanent colors will not fade
- Premium 100% Cotton Back / 100% Poly Front (print side)
- The weight of a towel is measured by the GSM (Grams per Square Meter). Low GSM (300-400) towels are light and thin whilst high GSM (450-600) towels are thicker and heavier.
- 22&quot; * 42&quot; Kid is 220 gsm
- 30&quot;* 60&quot; Microfiber is 220 gsm
- 30&quot;* 60&quot; Adult is 350 gsm
- 30&quot;* 60&quot; Premium is 450 gsm
- Easy to launder and maintains its softness after washing
- Machine Washable - Easy to care for (see care instructions below)
- Printed on one side, the opposite side is solid white
- 2 sizes, 22&quot; x 42&quot; and 30&quot; x 60&quot;

How To Order

1- Select your SIZE
3- Write your NAME


* Capitalization will be as pictured in sample photo unless specific note says otherwise.
* Please Note: All sizes have a variance +/- 1&quot;-2&quot; due to heat causing shrinking when pressed
* Please review photos for size references!*

Care Instructions

To keep the fibers soft and silky over time, it is very important to avoid fabric softeners when washing this beach towel. Many laundry pods contain softeners, and we recommend not using laundry pods for this item.

- Wash with detergent only, no fabric softeners
- Wash in cold water
- Gentle cycle
- Wash separately to avoid lint transfer from other textiles
- Tumble dry low and remove promptly
- Do not bleach or dry clean

ADDITIONAL NOTES

- Please keep in mind when ordering that color settings on monitors and lighting in product photography vary so the product might differ a tad from what you see on screen.
- I don''t accept returns, exchanges, or cancellations. But please contact me if you have any problems with your order.
- If you have any questions, please use the “Message Seller” button next to the price and I’ll get right back to you.

